Package org.jtimer.Exceptions

The package in which all custom exceptions are stored.

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DimensionsInvalidException
    Used if a Matrix doesn't have the necessary dimensions to execute the task at hand.
    NotProperlyInitializedException
    Used if an If object's Else method is executed before the Then method.

Package org.jtimer.Exceptions Description

The package in which all custom exceptions are stored. Most exceptions don't add any extra functionality, they are used to have more descriptive exceptions.
